Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬 晶馬…!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.25,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}くるくるまわる　君の瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:06.07,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}探してまわる　駅のホーム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:11.16,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}響くファンファーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.36,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ガラガラ音をたてる街
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.27,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}とりあえず　耳を貸してみたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:23.73,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　消えるはずの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.15,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:37.98,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もう二度と会えないような　そんな気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.35,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}運命が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.71,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}臨界点を突破してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.51,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}限界ならすでに去って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:53.84,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}絶対的支配だって　崩壊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:59.73,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}終末理論は机上の　空論でしかないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:10.29,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}0と1の世界線の果てから　叫ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:18.91,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}もうすぐ　君が会いに来るような気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:24.44,op_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕は目を閉じるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:13.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.25,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}轉啊轉 你的眼睛不停轉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:06.07,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在月台四處尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:11.16,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}號角聲在空中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.36,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}大街上轟轟作響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.27,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總之 先傾聽這聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:23.73,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在這個就要消逝的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.15,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:37.98,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總是覺得 我們無法再度相會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.35,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}命運也在嘲笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.71,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}突破臨界點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.51,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}極限已然消去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:53.84,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}就算被絕對地支配 也讓它崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:59.73,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}末日理論無非是一紙空談
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:10.29,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在0與1的世界線的盡頭 呼喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:18.91,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}總是覺得 你即將來與我相會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:24.44,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那我 就閉上眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉沒事的樣子 睡得像灘爛泥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說笨蛋不會感冒 看來也不會受傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣說沒關係麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥… 陽毬…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}小冠一接到醫院打來的電話 臉色就變得煞白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴 絕對不要告訴晶馬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經早上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要準備早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這裏是…醫院?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你就死在那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得昨天發生的事了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶被車撞到 就住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有記憶的話 就說明腦袋沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應有點慢那是天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有骨折 只是輕微磕碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生也笑著說你運氣好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 雖然小冠嘴上這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他從昨天開始就沒合過眼 一直陪在小晶的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我去叫蘋果過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶要好好向她道謝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘋果叫的救護車 一直寸步未離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶醒過來了哦 現在很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說想向蘋果道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 快點進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我沒有這個資格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 到底發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出的事故 還有荻野目蘋果的那件東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩者是有關聯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…你是被那女人撞出去的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是我又犯傻了呢 還是多管閒事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這純粹是偶然事故 不是她的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小冠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有收到過女孩子送的禮物麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷不丁地說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小冠很受歡迎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶說你是花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋 又對陽毬說奇怪的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子送你什麼樣的禮物 你會開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想從其他女孩子那裏得到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼特別想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的東西呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那倒是有很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如 會說「這是我傾注心意做成的」那類東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想 比如便當 就有人做得異常精緻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切得極其複雜的章魚小香腸之類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從斷面看還是花朵或動物圖案的壽司卷之類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 那種挺讓人毛骨悚然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 便當不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 大得出奇的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還放著穿婚紗的情侶娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個確實是來勢洶洶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只…只有這些?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 最受不了的還是手織毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還有超級顯眼的名字 那個太鬱悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在我被迫穿著它的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍巾之類的 你肯定也覺得麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 陽毬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛所說的 全部都是玩笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢對陽毬手織禮物挑三揀四的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上是不存在的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能收到陽毬送的圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼時候 什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是身處極熱的撒哈拉沙漠正中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會把人熱癱的熱帶雨林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會好好地圍給你看!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手織萬歲!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Viva 圍巾!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.76,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}viva，意大利語萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠 我會織得讓你圍得舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回家裏一趟 去取小晶的換洗衣物哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 小冠你就去陪陪小晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時發生的事情 你幫我瞞著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:08:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到冠葉和陽毬 真相就說不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝蓋…擦傷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的傷麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用感覺這麼愧疚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是什麼大不了的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住院什麼的 太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那時候 我也說了很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過已經沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 日記沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 今天我就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被撕破了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一半…被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天日記不是掉到馬路上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時被一個騎摩托車的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 得趕緊碾碎掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高倉 該吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還特地為你準備了美味甜點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一波未平 一波又起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真討厭 茶水沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱水室離這裏有點遠 你認識路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕你啊 高倉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友一直陪在身邊照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很叫人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 茶水…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 艾絲梅拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣引誘獵物上鉤的餌就到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 開始狩獵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說不見了 是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該是在吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回來的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是晶馬發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.75,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.2\frz14.092\fs40\pos(525,405)}把「日記的另一半」交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.75,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.2\frz14.092\fs40\pos(400,487)}不然的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.75,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fay0.2\frz14.092\pos(462,520)}高倉晶馬就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日記的另一半」?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:27.16,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA8A8A8&\pos(240,481)}補充：
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:27.16,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA8A8A8&\pos(358,545)}高倉晶馬他，現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.88,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,481)}補充：
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.88,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,545)}高倉晶馬他，現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用日記當作交換條件 到底是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有前半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說「被搶走了」 被誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來了一輛摩托車 硬搶走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 搖搖晃晃亂走差點被車撞的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被晶馬他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你不是在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是當然的嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是晶馬來救我 現在我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:19.36,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}咦 這裏曬的內褲不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個的話 晶馬就危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就趕緊…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 不這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:39.24,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay-0.2\frz339.596\pos(463,527)}高倉冠葉帶著「日記」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:39.24,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay-0.2\frz339.596\pos(403,561)}到C棟的屋頂上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬暫且還平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我們也不是全無辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哎呀哎呀 我的內褲不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}老太太 我們現在就幫您去找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件是從晶馬的手機發送過來的 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晶馬被關在這醫院的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還是你拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只剩一半 這也是陽毬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們所需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼 也絕對不能交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不拿去的話晶馬他就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會救出晶馬的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這個就由你來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是你就算要把晶馬耍得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不肯交給他的重要東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照說好的 我把「日記」拿來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露餡了麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我想起什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣也想不起來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣? 就算這樣也不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個穿起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有選擇的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給高倉冠葉的指示是個圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荻野目蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把日記拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 高倉晶馬就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把日記從那裏扔下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 桃果…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別給我胡搞了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊放了晶馬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於想起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那毛衣 很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然對你而言 鴿血色…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:01.08,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(741,660)}pigeon blood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴿子鮮血的艷紅色最適合不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說 你的目的是什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道日記的事!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對沿著阿里阿德涅的紅線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}古希臘神話中英雄忒修斯，用阿里阿德涅\N給的紅線破解了米諾斯的迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直找到這裏的虛偽的勇者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得表揚一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就告訴你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 那人是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同計劃的一樣 日記已到手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是期待接下來的發展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾絲梅拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:22.97,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(449,275)}請珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:22.97,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(811,275)}回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩獵才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 要把「M計劃」完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是那種會讓獵物逃走的愚蠢獵人喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存 戰略!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬利奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:54.96,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}10{\fs30\pos(640,630)}TH STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:54.96,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:16.11,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}全てがもし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:19.78,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}決められてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:28.80,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕らはどうして　もがくのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:32.96,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}それは、君じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:36.66,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}君の、せいじゃない
